Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.57,0:00:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,《德古拉》前情回顾…\NPreviously on Dracula...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,很荣幸能为你们举办订婚宴\NIt'll be my honor to host your engagement party.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.97,0:00:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都不同了\NThings will never be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你要结婚了  这才是问题所在\NYou are to be married, and that is that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她就是Ilona\NShe is Ilona.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不许你再提起Mina Murray\NYou must never again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.59,0:00:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,和我妻子长得像这事儿\Nmention Mina Murray's resemblance to my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你的血去创造血清\NI need your blood to create a serum
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这样你才能去征服阳光\Nso you are able to conquer daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.78,0:00:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你去查出\NI want you to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.07,0:00:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,关于Shaw将军的一切\Neverything about this General Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他是一个强大的对手\NHe's a powerful ally of my competitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道的\NVera Markham can tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,关于Shaw将军\Nall you need to know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.66,0:00:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Vera Markham会告诉你\Nabout Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你是？\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你想雇佣我\NYou wish to employ my services
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,让Renfield先生来解答一个问题\Nin order to get Mr. Renfield to answer one question.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！\NUnh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生  你在这儿干嘛？\NMr. Grayson. What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.93,0:01:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我不应该在这儿\NI know I shouldn't be here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但没时间了\Nbut there's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间干嘛？\NTime for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不  你必须离开  立刻  要不…\NNo. You must leave, immediately, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我会走的\NI'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.73,0:01:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证\NI promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.10,0:01:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但我必须告诉你\NBut I must tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.54,0:01:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你在犯一个错误\Nyou're making a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.47,0:01:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,严重的错误\NA terrible mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.51,0:01:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你什么意思？  - Harker\N- What do you mean? - Harker.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  他绝不会带给你快乐\NHe'll never be able to make you happy, and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎样这样说\NHow dare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没时间自欺欺人了  Mina\NNow is not the time for lies, Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.95,0:01:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这是真的\NYou know it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.92,0:01:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是  就说出来\NIf it isn't, say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我的眼睛  告诉我\NLook me in the eyes and say it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.96,0:01:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那我就走  - 不 不 不\N- and I'll go. - No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我爱…我爱Jonathan  不是别人\NI-I love... I love Jonathan, and no other,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他会成为我的丈夫\Nand he will be my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,整天都赖在床上\NOf all the days to lie-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道今晚前\NDon't you know we have a million things
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有一箩筐事情要做吗？\Nto do before tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 它仍继续？  - 当然仍在继续\N- It's still on? - Of course it's still on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你重新考虑\NUnless you've reconsidered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不  当然不是\NNo. No. No, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  看在上帝的面子上\NWell then, for goodness' sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,起来吧  亲爱的\Nget up, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这么重要的日子\NYou mustn't waste another second
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别浪费一分一秒啊\Nof this momentous day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.64,0:02:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你的婚宴在伦敦可是前无古人\NYours is going to be the most spectacular
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,盛世非凡呢\Nengagement party London has ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点儿  这很脆弱\NBe careful. That's very fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,来看看你的第一测试项目\NCome and meet your first test subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托用线把它和门连上\NPlace it in line with the door, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么东西不能有阴影！\NAnd no obstruction that may cast a shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会靠得太近的  教授\NI wouldn't get too close, Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你不认同\NI think you'll find her suitable,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得她挺合适\Nif not exactly agreeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿还有很多技术挑战\NThere are many technical challenges,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但我相信在给定时间内  我们会战胜它的\Nbut I believe we will surmount them, given time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,时间是奢侈的  我们没时间\NTime is a luxury we do not have.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须马上在阳光下行走\NI must walk in sunlight soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,人们起疑了\NPeople are getting suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你不明白吗？\NDo you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对了  Renfield去哪了？\NBy the way, where's Renfield?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他本应该在实验室\NHe was meant to accompany the lab equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,到处都找不到Renfield\NRenfield was nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才自己动手\NI had to do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Renfield先生\NMr. Renfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,来一个小旅程吧  就你和我\NWe are about to embark on a journey, you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,以一个问题为开端\NIt begins with a single question,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,以你的回答为终点\Nand it ends with your answer to that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,为了让你记住这点\NI want you to remember that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.43,0:04:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我再说一遍\Nso I will say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,以你的回答  为终点\NIt ends with your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你懂的  无论你觉得\NSo you see, no matter how helpless
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,多么无助  多么漫长\Nyou may feel, no matter how lengthy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,多么低贱  多么不悦\Ndebasing, and disagreeable
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这个“旅程”\Nthe journey may prove,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.16,0:04:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,最终  都是由你掌控\Nultimately, you are in control.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:05:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,能开始了吗？\NLet's get started, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的专业内  我深感自豪\NThough I take great pride in my profession,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然后来变得…\Nit has become...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,繁琐复杂\Ntedious of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可是  毕竟\NThere are, after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一不变的就是\Nonly so many variations
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以变着花样的玩儿\Non a theme one can play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,放了我\NRelease me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！\NUnh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  每一种用具都是独一无二的\NEach client is unique, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.26,0:05:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,方法各有迥异\NThe methods vary,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是结果必然相同\Nbut the result is inevitably the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我警告你\NI'm warning you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,后果很严重\Nthere will be repercussions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我常常想\NI often think,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,“也许这一次  Janina”\N"Perhaps this time, Janina.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,“就一次  仅此一次\N"This time, for once,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,“简单的回答了\N"The client will dispense with
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:05:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我的第一问\Nall the bluster and defiance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的咆哮和反抗\Nand simply answer the question
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,都将被免除”\Nthe first time I ask it."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander Grayson爱着谁？\NWho does Alexander Grayson love?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  好吧\NOh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也许得下次\NPerhaps next time.
