Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这是Shaw将军的个人账户\NThese are General Shaw's personal accounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,都在这儿了  所属Bellamy公司\NIt's all there, under Bellamy Limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellamy公司？\NBellamy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.09,0:07:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,帝国军火  唯一股东\NSole shareholder, empire munitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,帝国军火？\NEmpire munitions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Show从军火制造商那里收钱？\NShaw's receiving money from an arms manufacturer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,七月份  六万磅\N60,000 pounds in July.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,七月  就在那时…帝国中标了\NJuly, that's when... That's when the empire
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,八个新战舰\Nwon the tender for eight new warships.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他拿了佣金\NHe got commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaw将军这是受贿罪\NGeneral Shaw is taking bribes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker  请问\NHarker, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算如何处置这些信息？\NWhat do you plan to do with this information?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你拜托我操办这个派对\NI know you begged me to organize this party
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我也确实答应你了 但并不意味着\Nand I agreed, but that doesn't give you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你就可以当甩手姑奶奶了\Nthe right to be an idle princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你有宾客名单 我有回执\NYou have the guest list. I have the replies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你负责把这两个对照一下\NYou check the former against the latter,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,因为饭店明天中午前就要最终名单了\Nand the kitchen needs the final count by noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,宾客名单绝对出错了\NThis list, it's all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Davenport 爵士 Rothcoft爵士？\NLord Davenport. Lord Rothcroft?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是难以想到\NWho'd ever have guessed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan还有这样大牌的朋友呢？\Nthat Jonathan had such distinguished friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 可他们并不是他的朋友\NYes, but they're not his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,至少 他从来没向我提及过他们\NAt least, he's never mentioned them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕这都是我的错\NAll my doing, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是我坚持让他邀请那些巨头的\NI insisted he invite them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Grasyson 先生的盛情小女子有些承受不起\NIt's all rather overwhelming, Mr. Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,您不觉得您过于大包大揽了吗？\NAre you sure it's not too much of an imposition?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,绝非如此\NNot at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,都是Westenra小姐“法力无边”才让这\NThis is just an empty stage upon which Miss Westenra
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,才让这平凡的舞台变得妙不可言\Nhas lavished her formidable magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,总算有人欣赏我的苦劳了\NAt least somebody appreciates all my hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander! 你一定不会相信…\NAlexander! You won't believe what...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.31,0:08:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina.\NMina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,介意和我借一步说话吗？\NCould we have a word privately, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们  请原谅我们的失陪\NLadies, if you will excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.42,0:08:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaw绝对不是吃素的\NShaw is far from a saint, and I've got
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经找到了证明这个的依据\Nthe evidence to prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不要管他\NNot now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我已经开了个会  - 听我的 别插手\N- I've just had a meeting. - I said, leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy 将来你可能会觉得\NLucy, you'll probably think me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个被宠坏的孩子\Na spoiled child...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能\NImpossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么问题了吗？\NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了个这辈子最令人为难的梦\NI had the most perplexing dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那种梦  是吧？\NThat kind of dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不  才不是那种梦呢\NNo. Not that kind of dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我…\NTell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,梦里的Jonathan是比现在更谨慎呢\NWas the dream version of Jonathan more circumspect,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,还是有更宽厚的肩膀呢？\Nor was it merely a matter of circumference?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至都没…\NAnd it wasn't even...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这个梦无关Jonathan\NIt wasn't even Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是 我自然梦到的是Jonathan\NYes, of course. Of course it was Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Renfield  昨晚去Victoria 站点\NRenfield went to Victoria Station last night
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要取一些实验工具\Nto pick up some laboratory equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他没来\NHe never arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,从昨晚他就蒸发了\Nand he has not been heard from since.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能只是路上耽搁了\NWell, perhaps he was detained.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他都失踪九个小时了\NHe's been missing nine hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,要是耽搁了他会告诉我们\NHe would have sent word.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去联系警察吗？\NShall I contact the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 警方不能介入\NNo, no. No police.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这次绝对要做的完全不留痕迹\NThis must be handled with the utmost discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在公司的这个节骨眼上\NAt this point of our business,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson 能源承受不了任何丑闻\NGrayson Energy cannot afford a scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我确信您比任何人都了解这一点\NI'm sure you understand that more than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,自然如此\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那好  我从医院太平间开始排查\NWell, I'll start with the hospitals, the morgues.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他取设备前\NDid he have any appointments prior
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有提前说过要干啥了吗？\Nto picking up the equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就说去当地钢铁公司\NOnly to gather some information
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,收集些情报\Nfrom local steel mills.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  这样就略微缩小了范围\NWell, that narrows things down a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他可不是不显眼的人\NHe's hardly inconspicuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,让我一个人调查吧\NLeave it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan?\NJonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina 我现在必须失陪下\NI really must be going, Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,等等…名单真是对的？\NWa... Is this list right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我有些紧急公务不得不去\NI-I have some urgent business to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们稍后再讨论这个\NWe'll have to discuss this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可是今晚就是订婚夜了啊\NBut the party is tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就剩几个小时了\NIt's in a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  我是加了几个人  就这样\NWell, I-I made a few additions, is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,工作上的泛泛之交  以及诸如此类\NBusiness acquaintances and so forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我担心的不是加了几个人\NIt's not the additions that concern me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,而是你漏了的\Nit's the people you have disinvited.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,像是谁？\NLike who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,所有你在报社的朋友  比如Szabo\NAll your friends at the paper. Szabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Szabo?\NSzabo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina想象下  我们可是提供酒水的\NThink, Mina. We're serving alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的希望他来拿香槟杯子玩杂耍\NDo you really want him juggling champagne bottles
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:10:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,例行公事的跳小熊舞？\Nand doing his dancing bear routine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我确信他一定不会失态\NI'm sure he will behave himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不行！\NThe answer is no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在走向整个世界\NWe're moving up in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在这途中失去几个朋友\Nand its only natural that we're gonna lose
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,再自然不过了\Na few friends on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你内心真实的声音？\NWould you listen to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 还有谁要来？\NSo, who else will be in attendance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Rothcroft  还有其他几个人\NRothcroft. A few others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我真切的希望\NI do hope there won't be another
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚不要出啥大乱子\Ngrand spectacle this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,最好还是孤立\NBrash Americans like Grayson
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,像Grayson这种傲气的美国人\Nare best left twisting in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦他们发现钱不能收买一切\NOnce they realize their money can't buy cooperation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,除非被惹恼了  他们自己就会打包走人\Nthey pack up and move on... unless provoked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是自然  先生\NOf course, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只要没有您的吩咐\NThere should never be any direct action against
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,就不会直接对他用强\NGrayson without your express permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.57,0:11:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你会和Lucy一起呆在Carfax\NI thought you'd be at Carfax with Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来是\NI was,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我觉得我最好回家休息下\Nbut I thought I'd come home and rest a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你母亲一定会为你骄傲的\NYour mother would be so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你把Jonathan发掘成了一个好男人\NYou've found a fine man in Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,她一定会对你的选择高兴的\NI know she'd be happy with your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,可能她会更喜欢一个月前的\NA month ago, perhaps,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那个从前的Jonathan\Nwith the old Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但他变了\NBut he's changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么变的？\NIn what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  就从这开始吧\NWell, to start with,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他结交了一帮新朋友…\Nhe's got an entirely new set of friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,其中多数是商业伙伴…\Nbusiness associates, most of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他们是有爵位的富人\Nand they're titled and wealthy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,年纪比他大很多\Nand much older than he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这很平常啊\NThat's perfectly natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他转行了\NHe's in a new line,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,必然要结交新朋友\Nhe's bound to make new acquaintances.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这倒是  但他和多数老朋友断绝往来\NYes, but he's cut ties with most, if not all,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎他们的存在可有可无\Nof his old friends, as though they're expendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不禁想…\NAnd I can't help but think...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你也会变得可有可无?\NThat you might become expendable as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:13:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须承认  Renfield先生…\NI must admit, Mr. Renfield...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,您的耐力令人印象深刻\NYour stoicism is impressive,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但绝对算不上惊人\Nbut by no means a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Rodrigo?  - 不\N- Rodrigo? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你真坚强…\NOh, you are strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你很能吃苦\NAnd clearly no stranger to suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,无论在怎样的环境下\NAdmirable traits
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是令人钦佩的特质\Nunder virtually every other circumstance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,噢  Renfield先生\NAlas, Mr. Renfield,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样  至少此时此地别这样\Nnot here, not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就你我两人\NThere is just me and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你只需要…回答问题!\NThe question...and the answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander Grayson爱谁?\NWho does Alexander Grayson love?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Renfield被绑了\NRenfield's been abducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,谁干的?\NBy whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只能假设是恶龙会\NWe can only assume it's the Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但日落后\NBut until the sun goes down,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我才能救他\NI'm powerless to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为他们会撬开他的嘴?\NDo you think they can break him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他出卖我之前就会死\NHe will die before he says a word against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  那问题就解决了\NVery well, then. Problem solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不能让任何事\NWe cannot let anything
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,分散我们对实验的注意力\Ndistract us from today's test.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,总共需要多长时间?\NHow long will this entire process take?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我会用共鸣器\NI will use the resonator to generate voltage
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.57,0:14:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,给一对电桨生成电压\Nto a pair of electrical paddles,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:15:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,然后放入胸腔\Nthen apply them to the subject's chest
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,尝试让其产生心跳\Nand attempt to jolt the heart into beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,之后我会给她大剂量注射\NThen I will give the subject a massive injection of the serum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,如果成功\NIf it works,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你尽快将技术运用在我身上\Nyou will immediately repeat the whole process on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但我没有足够的血清\NBut I won't have an adequate supply of the serum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.22,0:15:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所以过程会比较缓慢\NAs you can see, it's a slow process.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有装备!\NI don't have the equipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\NHold a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 打扰一下  - 怎么了  先生?\N- Excuse me. - Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.88,0:16:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我找Havershim先生\NI'm looking for a Mr. Havershim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是生意\NIf it's business,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,联系圣路易斯办公室\Ncall my St. Louis office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我电联过圣路易斯办公室\NI have called your St. Louis office,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,堪萨斯城办公室\Nand your Kansas City office,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,以及卡森城办公室\Nand your Carson City office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.36,0:17:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,先别说  让我猜猜\NDon't tell me, let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你是Alexander Grayson\NYou're Alexander Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\NThat's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你想买我的斯威特沃特项目\NAnd you want to buy my Sweetwater operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还有双驾横木矿产\NAnd your Doubletree mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我出价\NI am willing to offer you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,两万美元\N20,000 of your American dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,当真?\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真令人印象深刻\NImpressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生  你要么是个勇敢的人\NMr. Grayson, you are either a very brave man
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.27,0:17:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要么就是个蠢蛋\Nor a very foolish one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,赤手空拳就敢过来\NThis is a rough country to be traveling unarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢枪\NI don't like guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这个时候买矿是一个\NThis is a singularly
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,非常不凑巧的时间  先生\Ninopportune moment to purchase a mine, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事?\NWhat the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦税率正在上调\NFederal taxes on minerals are set to escalate,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你坚持要买\Nso if you insist on making the purchase,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,提供一个售后回租条款\Nmake sure you tender an option
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可以减少损失\Nwith a leaseback provision to avoid the levies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  来点威士忌怎么样?\NWhiskey, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫?\NAnd what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Renfield. R.M. Renfield  先生\NRenfield. R.M. Renfield, esquire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander!\NAlexander!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的没错\NYou were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Renfield昨天下午四点左右\NRenfield was abducted outside of Empire and Colonial
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在殖民帝国外被捕了\Nyesterday afternoon around 4:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我问了一个新闻小贩\NI found a newspaper vendor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.30,0:18:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他目睹了整个过程\NHe witnessed the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 具体描述?  - 三个男人\N- Did he give a description? - Mm, three men.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.46,0:18:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,一个打他\NOne hit him, the others
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.27,0:18:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,另外两个抓住他扔进了马车\Ngrabbed him and threw him into a carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他通知警方了吗?\NDid he notify the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他以为那就是警察\NHe assumed it was the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我发现了这个\NI found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哪儿来的?\NWhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,大门外的水沟槽\NIn the gutter just outside the main entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,通知警方吗?\NShall I notify the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,有这个就够了\NThis is all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为\NI was beginning to think
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我得独自开始了\NI would be forced to start without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.73,0:19:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我有紧急事务要处理\NI had an urgent matter to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,还有比这更紧急的吗?\NAnd what could be more urgent than this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我终于有了Renfield的线索\NI finally have a lead on Renfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可以开始了吗?\NShall we proceed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,首先从心脏开始\NFirst, we start its heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,1,000伏  一圈\N1,000 volts, circuit one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,3,000伏!\N3,000 volts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,3,000伏  一圈\N3,000 volts, circuit one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有心跳了\NIt's beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了\NSuccess.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在不能走!\NYou can't leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须去找Renfield\NI must find Renfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.79,0:22:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你要举行一个派对\NYou are about to host a party
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.12,0:22:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,恶龙会的人都要出席\Nat which known members of the Order will be present.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,教授  如果你不想失去手臂\NProfessor, if you ever valued that arm,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就放开我\Ntake it off mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.73,0:22:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,马上!\Nimmediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.68,0:24:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.39,0:24:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢前来\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.89,0:24:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 马上回来  亲爱的  - 好的\N- Back in a tick, darling. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,见到你很高兴\NLovely to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.16,0:24:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我向他保证我不会跳得和熊一样\NI promised him I will not do my dancing bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.70,0:24:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我应该去照看一下女士们了\NI think it's time for me to see to the women.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.97,0:24:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你原谅我的失礼的话\NIf you will excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.74,0:24:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Jonathan  -Murray医生\N- Jonathan. - Dr. Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.21,0:24:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina  你看上去真漂亮\NMina, you look lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.41,0:24:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.69,0:24:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你是对的\NYou were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.69,0:24:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始忘记我是谁了\NI was beginning to forget who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.43,0:24:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会忘\NI never will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.40,0:24:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在你身边提醒你\NAnd I will always be here to remind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.40,0:24:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你保证？\NPromise?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.08,0:25:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望Grayson先生\NI hope Mr. Grayson likes
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.92,0:25:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢我们的的布置\Nwhat we've done with the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.18,0:25:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  他还没到么？\NWell, he... He hasn't arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.45,0:25:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  没  还没呢  他仍在途中\NMm-mm, no, not yet. He's still to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.12,0:25:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生爱谁呢？\NWho does Mr. Grayson love?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.23,0:25:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Renfield先生 他爱谁呢？\NMr. Renfield, who does he love?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.70,0:25:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander Grayson先生爱谁呢？\NWho does Mr. Alexander Grayson love?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.50,0:25:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意提供给你\NI am willing to offer you 20,000
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.24,0:25:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,20000美元\Nof your American dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.01,0:25:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生\NMr. Grayson,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.31,0:25:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你要么是个勇敢的人\Nyou are either a very brave man...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.94,0:25:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,要么就是个蠢蛋\Nor a very foolish one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.04,0:25:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,赤手空拳\NThis is a rough country
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.35,0:25:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就敢过来\Nto be traveling unarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.88,0:25:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这个时候买矿是一个\NThis is a singularly inopportune moment
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.44,0:25:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,非常不凑巧的时间  先生\Nto purchase a mine, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.19,0:25:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事?\NWhat the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.69,0:25:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,联邦税率正在上调\NFederal taxes are set to escalate,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.39,0:25:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你坚持要买\Nso if you insist on making the purchase,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.49,0:25:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,提供一个售后回租条款\Nmake sure you tender an option
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.79,0:25:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可以减少损失\Nwith a leaseback provision to avoid the levies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.46,0:25:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  来点威士忌怎么样?\NWhiskey, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.40,0:25:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.40,0:25:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想杀了你\NThey mean to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.90,0:26:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!\NUnh!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.20,0:26:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的够多了\NThat's enough outta you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.67,0:26:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你感觉自己很聪明么？  恩？\NYou think you're so smart? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.31,0:26:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧  伙计  一起吧\NCome on, boys! Join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.44,0:26:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,恩!\NUnh!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.20,0:26:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.45,0:26:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在安全了\NYou're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.12,0:26:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Renfield先生\NMr. Renfield?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.99,0:26:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Renfield先生\NMr. Renfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.66,0:27:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson爱谁呢？\NWho does Grayson love?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.76,0:28:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪了 没有指挥者的踪影呢\NCurious. No sign of the ringmaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.39,0:28:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,毫无疑问的是精心设计了他的大厅入口\NNo doubt choreographing his grand entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.56,0:28:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上我说的是他的手下\NI actually meant his man.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.86,0:28:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  那个大个头的家伙\NYou know, the very large one
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.10,0:28:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,总做些夸张演讲的的家伙\Nwho makes all the turgid announcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.30,0:28:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫什么来着？\NWhat's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.04,0:28:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,提到大厅入口\NSpeaking of grand entrances.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.87,0:28:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她在找Grayson\NShe's looking for Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.72,0:28:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的\NHow can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.81,0:28:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因为只有他不在\NBecause he's the only one who isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.65,0:28:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜的人啊\NPoor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.95,0:28:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,把她最好的青春\NSpent her best years
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.75,0:28:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,花在了她喜欢的男人身上\Nhaving any man she pleases,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.05,0:28:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在呢？\Nbut now?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.65,0:28:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wetherby小姐碰到了一个并不愉快的前景\NLady Wetherby faces the unpleasant prospect
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.52,0:28:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没有一个人是她内心想要的\Nof not having the one man she really wants
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.12,0:28:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,而他的丈夫又枯萎在病床上\Nwhile her husband withers away in his sickbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.08,0:29:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我为我的迟到表示歉意\NI apologize for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.85,0:29:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望一切都如您所想  Murray小姐\NI hope everything is as you wish, Miss Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.88,0:29:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢  为所有事\NThank you so much, for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.58,0:29:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.46,0:29:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你看上去很漂亮\NYou look very lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.23,0:29:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,请原谅我的失礼\NYou'll have to excuse me, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.46,0:29:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 顺便谢谢你  - 为什么？\N- Thank you, incidentally. - What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.13,0:29:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在你的帮助下\NWith your help,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.93,0:29:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们找到了Renfield的所在\Nwe managed to locate Renfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.57,0:29:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一言以蔽之  一切安好\NSuffice it to say, all is good,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.44,0:29:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管我还不知道谁应对此负责\Nthough I'm no closer to knowing who's responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.44,0:29:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他？  - 他没事  我向你保证\N- Is he... - He's quite all right. I assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.98,0:29:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,现在  关于Shaw将军\NNow, what's this interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.64,0:29:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么有趣的消息么？\Nnews you have regarding General Shaw?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.88,0:29:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 相当棒的宴会  - 恩\N- Quite the party. - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.85,0:29:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定是个很值钱的雇员\NHe must be a very valuable employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.96,0:29:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你感觉Harker怎么样？\NWhat do you think of Harker?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.86,0:29:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为他会很有用\NI think he could be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.10,0:29:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果一定要说点什么的话\NAnd if anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.40,0:29:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就是他有野心\Nhe's ambitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.03,0:29:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,当然你没考虑招募新人\NSurely you're not thinking of recruitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.50,0:29:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  他还不够老练\NWell, he's a little rough around the edges,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.27,0:29:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们总得用点新鲜血液\Nbut we could always use some fresh blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.50,0:30:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不列颠为对抗奥斯曼的战争武装得越多\NThe more Britain arms itself for war against the Ottomans,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.10,0:30:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaw将军以权谋私的就越多\Nthe more General Shaw stands to gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.54,0:30:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上这个国家做的每一笔交易\NOn virtually every munitions deal this country makes,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.41,0:30:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他都从中分成\Nhe's getting a cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.61,0:30:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,合同总价值的10%\N10% of the total value of the contracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.38,0:30:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker  这些指控\NHarker, these allegations...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.72,0:30:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不只这些指控\NMore than allegations.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.68,0:30:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我查了他的账户  他们很是小心\NI've checked his accounts. They're meticulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.49,0:30:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,听着  Harker\NLook, Harker,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.63,0:30:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意图是使他陷入窘境\Nmy intention was to embarrass the man,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.62,0:30:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是查他老底起诉他\Nnot have him dragged up on charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.96,0:30:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但Shaw是个伪君子\NBut Shaw's a hypocrite.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.93,0:30:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,身居高位的卖国贼\NA traitor of the highest order.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.40,0:30:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你也没暗示我放手此事  对吗？\NYou're not suggesting I just let this go, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.63,0:30:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\NAh.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.77,0:30:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生  还有新郎\NMr. Grayson, and the groom.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.07,0:30:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Jayne Wetherby女士\NLady Jayne Wetherby.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.31,0:30:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我邀请的她  希望你别介意\NI invited her. I hope you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.24,0:30:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不\NOf course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.14,0:30:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  失陪一下\NUm, if you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.88,0:30:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker.\NHarker.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.35,0:30:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你了\NI've missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.29,0:30:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来如此的秀色可餐\NYou look absolutely ravishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.83,0:31:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  那最好是赶紧就餐\NOh, far better to be ravished.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.10,0:31:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才自己去哪里了？\NWhere have you been keeping yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.10,0:31:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,貌似有人掳走\NIt seems somebody abducted
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.03,0:31:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,并折磨了我的人  Renfield\Nand tortured my man, Renfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.70,0:31:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  天啊\NOh, good lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.14,0:31:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会有人做那事?\NWhy would someone do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.28,0:31:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是一些过去的商业争斗\NProbably some old business rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.88,0:31:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心\NAnd don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.52,0:31:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,事情都已经解决了\NIt's all been resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.89,0:31:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可以吗  - 好\N- Shall we?  - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.39,0:31:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生?\NUh, Mr. Grayson?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.12,0:31:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,请许我把你介绍给我老板\NPlease let me introduce you to my employer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.33,0:31:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生  哦  Wetherby女士\NUh, Mr. Grayson, um, Lady Wetherby,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.16,0:31:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是Browning先生\Nthis is Mr. Browning.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.83,0:31:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Browning先生  - Grayson先生\N- Mr. Browning. - Mr. Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.63,0:31:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- Davenport大人  - 我们见过\N- Lord Davenport. - We've met.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.47,0:31:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rothcroft大人\NLord Rothcroft.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.54,0:31:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Rothcroft大人  - Grayson先生\N- Lord Rothcroft. - Mr. Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.80,0:31:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 还有Godalming大人  - Godalming大人              -\N- And Lord Godalming. - Lord Godalming.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.01,0:31:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来我家\NWelcome to my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.17,0:31:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴你能邀请我们\NVery kind of you to have us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.34,0:31:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们  请原谅我们\NUh, gentlemen, please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.45,0:32:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我等不及去认识你了\NI cannot wait to get you to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.12,0:32:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你会的\NHmm, and so you shall.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.46,0:32:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生\NMr. Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.51,0:32:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰一下  Grayson先生?\NExcuse me, Mr. Grayson?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.95,0:32:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你见见我的导师和朋友\NI would like you to meet my mentor and my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.62,0:32:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Van Helsing教授\NProfessor Van Helsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.78,0:32:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,见到你真高兴\NIt's a pleasure to meet you,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.66,0:32:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Van Helsing教授\NProfessor Van Helsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.12,0:32:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,很荣幸见到你\NHonored to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.12,0:32:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,教授可是其领域的先驱啊\NThe Professor is a pioneer in his field.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.22,0:32:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\NIs that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.37,0:32:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson的人  Renfield被绑架了\NGrayson's man, Mr. Renfield, was abducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.80,0:32:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 真的?  - 是真的\N- Really? - Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.77,0:32:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,被绑走和虐待?\NAbducted and tortured.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.74,0:32:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是组织干的吗？\NWas that Order business?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.31,0:33:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是\NAbsolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.68,0:33:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生一直都很热心\NMr. Grayson's been kind enough to give us
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.38,0:33:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,为我们今晚的庆祝提供他的房子\Nhis home for our celebration tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.38,0:33:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他确实非常慷慨\NHow remarkably generous of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.15,0:33:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  教授  乐意效劳\NThank you, Professor. A pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.19,0:33:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Murray小姐\NMiss Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.77,0:33:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了教授?\NProfessor?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.28,0:33:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一切还好吗?\NIs everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.01,0:33:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,失陪一下\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.73,0:33:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  先生们女士们\NAll right, ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.13,0:33:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,为了我漂亮\NFor my beautiful daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.35,0:33:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,又让我总是骄傲的女儿Mina\NMina, who has always made me proud,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.80,0:33:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我一直看做是儿子的Jonathan\Nand for Jonathan, who I have long considered a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.43,0:33:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina  我  希望你母亲能在这儿\NMina, I only wish your mother were here
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.04,0:34:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,见证你变成的那个女人\Nto witness the woman that you've become.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.11,0:34:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,请和我一起\NPlease, join me
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.29,0:34:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,为这对儿快乐的夫妻举杯\Nin raising a glass to the happy couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.91,0:34:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,为Mina和Jonathan\NTo Mina and Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.38,0:34:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,为Mina和Jonathan!\NTo Mina and Jonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.52,0:34:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们\NUh, ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.79,0:34:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚我想…\NI'd, um, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.87,0:34:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我想从感谢Murray医师开始\NI would like to start by thanking Dr. Murray,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.13,0:34:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅仅是为他亲切的言词\Nnot just for his kind words this evening
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.50,0:34:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,还有他终生的善良热心\Nbut for a whole lifetime of kindness,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.30,0:34:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,并允许我娶他的女儿来结束!\Nculminating in him allowing me to marry his daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.47,0:34:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我说"允许"  但是\NI say "Allowing," But,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.09,0:34:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,恩  任何了解Mina的人\Num, anyone who knows Mina
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.48,0:34:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,都知道她只走自己认定的道路\Nknows that she follows her own path,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.71,0:34:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,而那条路…\Nand that path...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.13,0:34:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那条指引她去使我这个\Nthat path has led her to make me
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.52,0:34:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,最最快乐幸运的人活着的道路\Nthe very happiest and very luckiest man alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.39,0:34:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,听  听\NHear, hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.75,0:34:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生!\NMr. Grayson!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.22,0:34:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚的欢宴堪称盛景\NTonight's festivities are nothing short of spectacular.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.69,0:34:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我已经苦苦思索良久\NNow I've thought long and hard about
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.06,0:34:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如何最好地去表达\Nhow best to express
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.09,0:34:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我对你的感激之情\Nmy gratitude to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.93,0:35:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,最后  我决定为你提供对我来说\Nand in the end, decided that it's right for me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.77,0:35:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,最最珍贵的东西…\Nto offer you what I consider most precious...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.04,0:35:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,第一曲舞的特权\NThe privilege of the first dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.07,0:37:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,能换我吗？\NMay I cut in?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.88,0:37:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我得透透气\NExcuse me. I need some air.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.25,0:37:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson有个秘密  我能看得出来\NGrayson has a secret. I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.99,0:37:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那会是什么？\NAnd what might that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.46,0:37:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我不完全确定\NI'm not entirely sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.20,0:37:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个没有档案的神秘家伙\NHe's a man of mystery without biography.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.83,0:37:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  对于一个美国人来说那是很寻常的\NWell, that's hardly unusual for an American.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.83,0:37:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那些反对他的人经常最后成死鬼了\NThose who oppose him frequently end up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.24,0:37:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那些经常反对你的\NThose that oppose you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.35,0:37:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,最后经常也会以死告终\Nfrequently end up dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.77,0:38:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是巧合  再无其它\NIt's coincidence. Nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.94,0:38:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,说到\NSpeaking of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.15,0:38:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他来到伦敦\Nhis arrival in London
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.75,0:38:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,牵涉到了一些非常不吉利的东西\Ncoincided with something rather more ominous.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.28,0:38:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个？\NWhich is?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.92,0:38:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你搜寻的老东西出现了\NThe advent of the old one you seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.79,0:38:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你带来了那老东西的骨灰  在罐子里\NI brought you the old one's ashes in a jar.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.49,0:38:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？\NDid you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.86,0:38:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander Grayson  一个吸…\NAlexander Grayson, a vamp...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.93,0:38:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,荒谬  不可能\NRidiculous. Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.27,0:38:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会是第一个\NYou would not be the first woman
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.27,0:38:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,被欲望蒙蔽眼睛的女人\Nto be blinded by desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.17,0:38:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,第一个猎人  是的…\NThe first huntsman, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.91,0:38:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但不是第一个女人\Nbut not the first woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.90,0:39:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开!\NGo away!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.22,0:40:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我在纽约获悉这儿的很多消息\NA lot of information I learned here in New York
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.19,0:40:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我在Charles Remick学法律时\Nwhile I was studying law
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.83,0:40:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一个主张废除死刑的人\Nunder Charles Remick, a white abolitionist.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.47,0:40:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,提议我在密苏里酒吧接受考试\NHe made a motion I be examined under the Missouri bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.67,0:40:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜测你通过了\NI presume you passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.34,0:40:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我加入了圣路易斯的一家公司\NI joined a firm in St. Louis
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.91,0:40:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,而且被送到西部\Nand was sent out west
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.17,0:40:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,去处理反索赔的事\Nto sort out a cross-claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.48,0:40:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,委托人反对我的种族\NThe client took exception to my race.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.91,0:40:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我为自己辩护\NI was set upon by ruffians,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.95,0:40:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我被恶棍袭击  而且被囚禁\Nand imprisoned for the crime of defending myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.92,0:40:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,圣路易斯的公司怎么说?\NWhat about the firm in St. Louis?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.45,0:40:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他们和我摆脱了关系\NWell, they washed their hands of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.49,0:40:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我怀疑他们一直都这样想的\NI suspect that was their intent all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.53,0:40:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,无亲无友  身无分文\NI was left friendless and penniless.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.60,0:40:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,只能说…\NSuffice to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.70,0:40:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,事情并未按计划进行\Nthings did not go to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.28,0:40:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对这一切我心存感激  先生\NI'm very grateful for this, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.01,0:41:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你别介意我问一句\NI hope I don't undermine that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.56,0:41:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,“为什么？”\Ngratitude by asking, "Why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.12,0:41:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你是一名高水准的律师  Renfield\NYou're a lawyer of the highest caliber, Renfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.59,0:41:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要一名律师\NI require a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.77,0:41:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我太了解流浪的滋味儿了\NI too know what it's like to live as an outcast,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.90,0:41:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我外表看起来高端大气\Noutside what passes for polite society,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.09,0:41:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,其实不然\Nbut rarely is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.37,0:41:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对超乎你的想象\NMore than you could possibly imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.11,0:41:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谜一样的男人  Grayson先生\NYou are a man of secrets, Mr. Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.65,0:41:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能这样说\NThat much, I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.08,0:41:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但为了我的职业操守\NBut I owe it to my profession and my good name
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.11,0:41:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,和职业信誉  我得说\Nto tell you that I can only work for a man
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.33,0:41:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我只为完全信任的人工作\Nwho trusts me completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.51,0:42:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那我告诉你我所有的秘密\NThen you shall know all my secrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.08,0:42:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你的人生将从此改变\Nand your life will never be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.89,0:42:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这算承诺吗？\NIs that a promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,310)\c&H0BE7EA&\fn华文新魏\fs24}12年前
